<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-460] document statfs functionality for project quotas</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-460</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Document the project quota functionality for &quot;&lt;tt&gt;df&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; and &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lfs df&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; when being run on a directory with project quota assigned.  This will return the amount of space available to that project rather the total filesystem space, if the project quota limit is smaller.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
